      <title>经济和地区动荡给伊朗大选蒙上阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/iran-s-election-overshadowed-by-economic-and-regional-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[37 岁的玛丽亚姆是德黑兰的一名健身教练，她过去常常为了选举而将对伊朗政客的蔑视放在一边，因为她的选票可以帮助带来变革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/iran-s-election-overshadowed-by-economic-and-regional-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 02:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
