    <item>
      <title>玻利维亚领导人否认发动政变以提高民众支持率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/bolivian-leader-denies-he-staged-coup-in-bid-to-boost-popularity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玻利维亚总统否认他为了提高自己的声望而发动了一场推翻其政府的戏剧性政变，并驳斥了一位被拘留的将军的说法，后者称他是根据行政命令领导起义的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/bolivian-leader-denies-he-staged-coup-in-bid-to-boost-popularity</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 01:33:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在 2024 年大选辩论中败给特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/biden-trump-spar-over-economy-in-their-first-debate-of-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登在周四的总统辩论中表现磕磕绊绊，这一表现有可能加剧人们对他年龄的担忧，并加剧民主党对其候选人能否在11月的大选中击败共和党人唐纳德·特朗普的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/biden-trump-spar-over-economy-in-their-first-debate-of-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 01:19:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
