      <title>欧盟领导人称格鲁吉亚入盟进程实际上已停止</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/eu-leaders-say-georgia-s-membership-process-effectively-halted</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟领导人表示，格鲁吉亚拒绝扭转对公民社会的镇压，已导致其加入欧盟的努力“事实上”停止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/eu-leaders-say-georgia-s-membership-process-effectively-halted</guid>
