    <item>
      <title>马克龙和肖尔茨劫持峰会的举动激怒了欧盟领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/macron-and-scholz-s-summit-hijack-hits-a-wall-of-angry-eu-leaders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国和德国习惯于在欧盟舞台上为所欲为。但当欧盟最大的两个经济体周四出席至关重要的欧盟峰会时，却因国内问题而分心，他们发现很难再施展影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/macron-and-scholz-s-summit-hijack-hits-a-wall-of-angry-eu-leaders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 21:43:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国拒绝联合防务拨款，激怒欧盟领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/germany-irks-eu-leaders-by-opposing-talks-on-how-to-fund-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国敦促欧盟领导人放弃有关联合国防开支的措辞，尽管其他成员国表示反对，他们认为需要额外的资源来提升欧盟的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/germany-irks-eu-leaders-by-opposing-talks-on-how-to-fund-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 15:28:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国以腐败为由开除两名前国防部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/china-expels-former-defense-minister-from-party-on-corruption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国执政的共产党以腐败指控为由开除了两名前国防部长，结束了在国防部门发生一系列清洗事件后人们对他们命运的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/china-expels-former-defense-minister-from-party-on-corruption</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 10:08:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾警告不要前往中国，称中国威胁“分裂分子”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/taiwan-warns-against-non-essential-travel-to-china-hk-macau-lxx3hnd4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾已将前往中国的旅行警告提升至第二高级别，理由是北京决定扩大对岛内“分裂分子”判处死刑的法律范围。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/taiwan-warns-against-non-essential-travel-to-china-hk-macau-lxx3hnd4</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 10:01:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟领导人选择冯德莱恩继续担任欧盟委员会主席</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/eu-leaders-set-to-pick-von-der-leyen-as-bloc-s-executive-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟领导人提名乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩连任欧盟执行机构主席，这是就未来五年任期最高职位达成的协议的一部分。]]></description>
